{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8e3cd3cd46","title":"致周恩来、博古电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3265b33461","index":0,"year":1936,"month":12,"day":24,"articleId":"8e3cd3cd46"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"565c30a42f","name":"博古","type":"人物"},{"id":"bcecfeaa3a","name":"叶剑英","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-2","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f373cdd8a7","type":"paragraph","text":"致周恩来、博古电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8e3cd3cd46"},{"id":"93e386e4fe","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年12月24日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8e3cd3cd46"},{"id":"59a131f68c","type":"paragraph","text":"对临时军政委员会名单，我们方面拟参加朱德、彭德怀、贺龙、叶剑英、徐向前五人。恩来、伯渠参加实际工作不参加名单，以以便将来进行国民党工作。泽东不参加。对张、杨说明，共产党为争取全国各派，应采此种方针，对张、杨亦是有利的。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8e3cd3cd46"},{"id":"f3f46b90d7","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]这是毛泽东和洛甫（张闻天）致周恩来、博古（秦邦宪）电的主要内容。博古是12月23日和叶剑英等一起到西安协助周思来工作的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8e3cd3cd46"}],"page":{"id":"493bf8f9ad","publicationId":"maoquanji9-2","articleId":"8e3cd3cd46","start":213,"end":213}}}},"__N_SSG":true}